    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in flawless condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always keeping it garage-tucked and professionally detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. It\u2019s ready for a new adventure, and I just know you\u2019re going to love driving it as much as I have!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
