    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing service and subframe reinforcement have been proactively completed. The chassis remains taut with OEM bushings and a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero panel gaps or oxidation. A true driver\u2019s machine with a crisp 6-speed manual linkage and a pristine undercarriage, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Spotless interior. Mechanically perfect. Clean title. Serious buyers only.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom-ready condition that defies its age. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored in a climate-controlled garage since day one. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented single-owner history with every service performed on schedule at the flagship dealership. From the crisp responsiveness of the engine to the factory-fresh feel of the suspension, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot. Complete with all original manuals, two keys, and the original window sticker, this is an investment-grade example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an extraordinary example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been maintained to the highest standards of preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to aesthetic and mechanical perfection. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality specimen that performs with the precision of a new machine. Comprehensive service documentation is available to verify its superior maintenance history.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such pristine condition that it practically still has that new-car smell! It runs like an absolute dream and looks stunning from every angle\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single flaw. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a collector-grade example of the celebrated S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with the high-pressure Double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies operating in flawless synchronization. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield reflects a life of climate-controlled preservation. This is a mechanically superior specimen, free of the typical wear patterns found in high-revving performance machines, offering a pure, analog driving experience.",
